  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-3ef9c03c-7fff-54b9-e0a7-ec1d348f3c01&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;By reason of the scale and subsequent massing of the proposed fourth floor roof extension, which would breach the height of adjacent roof level enlargements, combined with the creation of an uncharacteristic roof terrace at that level, the proposal would erode the character and appearance of the Hoxton Conservation, resulting in less than substantial harm to the significance of this heritage asset. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; white-space-collapse: preserve; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;No public benefits have been identified that would outweigh the level of harm caused. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;The development would, therefore, conflict with&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt; the relevant tests of the NPPF, Policies D1, D3, D4 and HC1 of the London Plan (2021), Policies LP1 and LP3 of the Hackney Local Plan 2033, and the guidance as contained within the Councilâs &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-style: italic; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
